{"id": 591, "genre": 1001, "title": "你无法忍受哪种文艺（腔）青年？", "description": "当文艺青年变成一个贬义词之后。", "record_count": 8651, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183507v4laRkFqLnP7hJmj.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-10-22T11:27:24Z", "options": [{"id": 21248, "content": "生生把自己过成林黛玉，幽怨的小眼神由衷的激发了鸡皮疙瘩——矫情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 275891}, {"id": 19203, "content": "你不懂我的世界", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 258279}, {"id": 19717, "content": "去咖啡馆必晒朋友圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 266530}, {"id": 19207, "content": "滤镜修图可不算啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136426}, {"id": 19208, "content": "装、装、装；朋友圈照片多数是带咖啡带书带一段复制来的话滤镜是一定的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263412}, {"id": 19209, "content": "不总用大白话好好说话，聊个天对白像演电影一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263416}, {"id": 19721, "content": "有点假的感觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 180230}, {"id": 19210, "content": "说的每一句话都玄之又玄 没法聊下去", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 211817}, {"id": 21771, "content": "不以物喜 不以己悲", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 191648}, {"id": 19469, "content": "谢邀", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259385}, {"id": 19982, "content": "根本没经历过什么就悲伤悲伤悲伤…闲得！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 234048}, {"id": 19727, "content": "明明很懂却装作朦胧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 266588}, {"id": 19472, "content": "我想说 卧槽", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 264985}, {"id": 19219, "content": "表面文静，其实心中早已澎湃", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263457}, {"id": 19220, "content": "分不清场合 拿不清尺度", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263463}, {"id": 23062, "content": "穿紧身裤戴眼镜的男人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 290286}, {"id": 23830, "content": "怎么总有种葡萄酸的感觉，都歇歇吧，很无趣的话题。自己明白就好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 294013}, {"id": 19993, "content": "成天伤感", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 221749}, {"id": 19227, "content": "忘了自己本来是什么样子", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263461}, {"id": 20764, "content": "空间里发个说说都说的是一些让人一知半解的话，每次碰到这种人都怀疑他自己是不是能看懂自己发的东西！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 271907}, {"id": 21533, "content": "逗比", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 277593}, {"id": 19231, "content": "做所谓文艺的事，做烂俗不堪的人。人都没做好，文艺会着边吗。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256806}, {"id": 20511, "content": "复制狗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1220487}, {"id": 21538, "content": "我经历了太多?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278659}, {"id": 19235, "content": "为了发自拍而强行附加一句看似文艺/忧伤/迷茫/淡定/看破红尘的话！实在找不到可以附加的就学明星发一句“晚安了！”“10月，你好”“好久不见，你们想我了吗？”明星们是因为工作因为身份！你真以为你有几千万粉丝呢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263503}, {"id": 42275, "content": "日漫控，韩国明星控", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 429564}, {"id": 19236, "content": "修图自拍。说说鸡汤。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263525}, {"id": 19237, "content": "逼装爆了还要撑", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 211486}, {"id": 19493, "content": "其实挺不容易的，你永远不知道他放出的这张照片是摆了多久姿势，编了多少句酸文，然后从多少千张选出来的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 221818}, {"id": 19238, "content": "就是特别的爱装的那种，明明什么都不懂。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 226933}, {"id": 101927, "content": "借文艺之名，行约pao之实", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692453}, {"id": 20008, "content": "好烦~", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 191029}, {"id": 19241, "content": "上面好多人心理过于阴暗", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256417}, {"id": 19242, "content": "不懂装懂啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263555}, {"id": 19243, "content": "觉得自己懂很多，自以为是", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263557}, {"id": 29739, "content": "谁也没有资格去评判别人，你又没有经历别人的人生", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 329901}, {"id": 19245, "content": "我最受不了的就是那种文艺+愤青…本来就没什么眼见…还特别激愤,觉得自己懂很多。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263593}, {"id": 20525, "content": "我", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 266172}, {"id": 19249, "content": "英语才过四级的文艺青年，微信朋友圈晒各种英语，见面又说不出几句…", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 258601}, {"id": 19250, "content": "对世界充满了不满，对人性充满了透彻的厌恶，对自己却充满了爱恋", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 131830}, {"id": 19251, "content": "用那种自以为很厉害很文艺的话语让你憋不出一句话。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263683}, {"id": 19508, "content": "（一）开题立即引经据典，卖弄学问的一种人     （二）作协头衔的另一种人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 265224}, {"id": 19254, "content": "单反", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263687}, {"id": 19766, "content": "知道的不多还非要全说", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211318gipX6de7KoQyOWY5.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 266844}, {"id": 20023, "content": "炫富的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 225182}, {"id": 19257, "content": "我就是文青，正在装逼现场....", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236693}, {"id": 18746, "content": "在公路铁路中央和草丛里不停地自拍", "image": null, "praise_count": 409, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 19258, "content": "每个都想赞，周围能装的人太多了，各种型都有", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 92856}, {"id": 18747, "content": "写情诗", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 19259, "content": "张口就看不惯这个 受不了那个 和日常从不真正翻书阅读的低头党☝️。", "image": "img/option/option/201606052113148VXm4s7BESAGIyqp.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263793}]}